default&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
defaultpromote and lead cultural change in relation to equalities and diversity
default 
default•
default&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
defaultengage staff at all levels with improving the promotion of equality and diversity
default•
default&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
defaultensure all members of the research workforce are trained and
default supported to address  disincentives and indirect obstacles to recruitment, retention and progression in research careers
default•
default&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
defaultprovide evidence of ways in which equality and diversity issues are managed at both
default 
defaultan institutional and department level
