defaultWhy do num
defaultbers of women in STEM academic careers decline further up the career ladder?
default&#xa0;
defaultWhen women leave academia, what careers do they transition into? What 
defaultare the consequences of scientifically trained women applying their skills in different employment sectors?
defaultWhat should universities and the higher education sector do to retain women graduates and PhD students in academic careers? Are there examples of good practice?
default&#xa0;
defaultWhat role should the Government have in encouraging the retention of women in academic STEM careers? 
